%% Classical GoF Observer — Subject keeps a list of Observer references
%% and calls `update()` on each when state changes.
classDiagram
    class Subject {
        -observers: List~Observer~
        +attach(Observer)
        +detach(Observer)
        +notify()
    }
    class Observer {
        <<interface>>
        +update(event)
    }
    class Logger
    class Emailer
    class Metrics

    Subject --> "*" Observer : notifies
    Observer <|.. Logger
    Observer <|.. Emailer
    Observer <|.. Metrics

    note for Subject "In Rust this becomes\nArc&lt;Mutex&lt;Vec&lt;Box&lt;dyn Observer&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;\nor similar. Four layers of indirection.\nEach .notify() locks, iterates,\nand dynamically dispatches."
